&lt;p&gt;This role sits within our Teads Studio APAC team, based in our Singapore office and reporting directly to the Head of Design of Teads Studio, APAC. Teads Studio is our in-house creative hub, responsible for helping global brands transform standard assets into rich, interactive, and highly engaging digital video and display formats. You will join a dynamic, cross-regional team of designers, developers, and creative strategists working collaboratively to get the absolute best out of our clients&#39; assets when activating campaigns on Teads across APAC.&lt;/p&gt;
