&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scope of Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;: Take hands-on ownership of digital graphic assets, video editing, motion design, and high-quality presentation decks to showcase concepts to clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact Metric&lt;/strong&gt;: Success in this role means producing premium creative mockups and interactive ad units that meet strict technical specifications and client guidelines within agreed-upon SLAs over the next 12 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Creative Innovation &amp;amp; Design&lt;/h4&gt;
