&lt;li&gt;Transform Client Assets: Re-imagine and repurpose static client assets (images, storyboards, and video files) into beautiful, rich, and mobile-optimized digital ad formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design Outcome Perfection: Ensure all creative executions are strictly aligned with our clients&#39; brand guidelines, color palettes, and style standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design Premium Pitches: Support our design and creative strategy teams in building elegant, highly visual, and client-ready PowerPoint presentation decks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Execution &amp;amp; Flawless Delivery&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Creative Asset Production: Manage day-to-day graphic asset preparation, video cutting, and motion transitions using Photoshop, After Effects, Illustrator, Premiere Pro, and Figma.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure Technical Accuracy: Validate that all creative files strictly comply with Teads’ technical specifications, file-size limits, and mobile deployment guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
